💡 Dynamic Bulb Project

A simple yet interactive **Dynamic Bulb** web app built using | HTML | CSS | JavaScript |. It simulates a real-life bulb that can be turned **ON** and **OFF** with a button click.


---

 📋 Features

- 🟢 Turn the bulb ON  
- ⚫ Turn the bulb OFF  
- ✨ Smooth visual transition  
- 🖥️ Responsive for all devices

---

 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5 – Basic structure  
- CSS3 – Styling and transitions  
- JavaScript – Dynamic control of bulb behavior  

